---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Sula Catering Vancouver | Award-Winning Indian Catering for Weddings, Corporate & Private Events"
	description="Vancouver's most trusted Indian catering company since 2010. Award-winning wedding catering, corporate lunches, and private party catering across the Lower Mainland. Halal, vegetarian, vegan menus."
	canonical="/"
>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/vancouver-catering-sula-indian-restaurant.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<p class="gold-label">Award-Winning Since 2010</p>
			<h1>The Art of <em>Indian Catering</em><br/>in Vancouver</h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">From intimate gatherings to grand weddings — flawlessly executed, exquisitely presented, and rooted in 15 years of craft.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Begin Your Event</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">A Heritage of Hospitality</p>
				<h2>Where Tradition Meets <em>Refinement</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p>Sula has been Vancouver's most trusted Indian catering name for over fifteen years — known for meticulous attention to detail, unwavering reliability, and an uncompromising commitment to flavour. Every event is led by a dedicated coordinator. Every dish, prepared with the same care we bring to our four award-winning restaurants across Vancouver.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp" alt="Indian food catering Vancouver Burnaby Richmond" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">What We Offer</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:48px;font-weight:400">Catering for Every <em style="color:var(--gold)">Occasion</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="services-grid">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card reveal">
					<div class="service-icon">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke-width="1.2"><path d="M24 8 C24 8 14 16 14 26 C14 32 18 38 24 40 C30 38 34 32 34 26 C34 16 24 8 24 8 Z"/><circle cx="24" cy="26" r="4"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Weddings</h3>
					<p>Elegant menus for sangeet, ceremony, and reception. Custom-built with your chef.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Discover →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card reveal delay-100">
					<div class="service-icon">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke-width="1.2"><rect x="10" y="14" width="28" height="24"/><path d="M18 14 V8 H30 V14"/><line x1="10" y1="22" x2="38" y2="22"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Corporate</h3>
					<p>Boardroom lunches and conferences delivered with zero-delay precision.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Discover →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card reveal delay-200">
					<div class="service-icon">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke-width="1.2"><path d="M14 24 L24 14 L34 24 L24 34 Z"/><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="4"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Private Parties</h3>
					<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, milestones — feasts that bring people together.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Discover →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card reveal delay-300">
					<div class="service-icon">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke-width="1.2"><path d="M14 18 H32 V30 C32 34 28 36 23 36 C18 36 14 34 14 30 Z"/><path d="M32 22 H36 C38 22 38 28 36 28 H32"/><line x1="20" y1="10" x2="20" y2="14"/><line x1="26" y1="10" x2="26" y2="14"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Café & Chai</h3>
					<p>Live chai stations, specialty coffee, and freshly baked goods.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Discover →</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/weddinf-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Sula wedding catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">The Sula Experience</p>
					<h2>Crafted with <em>Care.</em><br/>Served with <em>Soul.</em></h2>
					<p>Every menu begins with a conversation. We listen — to your story, your guests, your dreams for the day. Then our chefs build something exclusively yours, drawing from the regional cuisines of India and the discipline of fifteen years catering Vancouver's finest occasions.</p>
					<p>From halal-certified meats to pure-vegetarian, vegan, and Jain menus, every dietary need is met without compromise.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item">
							<div class="stat-number">15+</div>
							<div class="stat-label">Years</div>
						</div>
						<div class="stat-item">
							<div class="stat-number">2,000+</div>
							<div class="stat-label">Events</div>
						</div>
						<div class="stat-item">
							<div class="stat-number">4</div>
							<div class="stat-label">Locations</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="image-banner" style="background-image: url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp');">
		<div class="image-banner-content reveal">
			<h2>Authentic Flavours, <em>Effortless Service</em></h2>
			<p>From boardroom to ballroom — we handle every detail.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Recent Events</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:48px;font-weight:400">Moments <em style="color:var(--gold)">Worth Celebrating</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="gallery-grid">
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-bc-canada.webp" alt="Indian food catering Vancouver BC Canada" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-100"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/indian-catering-near-me-vancouver.webp" alt="Indian catering near me Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-200"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Office catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-300"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/indian-catering-near-me-vancouver-birthdays-parties.webp" alt="Indian catering for birthdays Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top:60px">
				<a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-plum">View Full Gallery</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="testimonial-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">A Word From Our Hosts</p>
				<p class="testimonial-quote">Sula didn't just cater our wedding — they made it unforgettable. Every guest still talks about the food, and our coordinator made the entire day effortless.</p>
				<p class="testimonial-author">— Priya & Arjun · Wedding for 350 Guests</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Service Areas</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:42px;font-weight:400">Catering Across the <em style="color:var(--gold)">Lower Mainland</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p style="font-size:18px;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto 40px;color:rgba(50,34,28,0.8)">Vancouver · North Vancouver · Burnaby · Richmond · Surrey · West Vancouver — reliable, beautifully executed Indian catering for events of any size, from intimate gatherings to weddings of 500+ guests.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="gallery-grid-3">
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/weddin-catering-burnaby-vancouver.webp" alt="Wedding catering Burnaby Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-100"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/indian-catering-vancouver.webp" alt="Indian catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-200"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-catering-vancouver-for-private-parties-birthdays-celebrations.webp" alt="Indian catering Vancouver private parties" loading="lazy" /></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<p class="gold-label" style="color:var(--gold-light)">Begin the Conversation</p>
			<h2>Let's Plan Something <em>Extraordinary</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
